original: intros m x y n. set (m1 := L m one x y). set (y0 := cA m zero y). set (MAX := MF.degree m x + MF.degree m y0). intro Hinv. intro Hnexp. intro Hle. assert (Hdeg := degree_L1_merge_MAX m x y). unfold m1, y0, MAX in Hdeg. specialize Hdeg with (inv_hmap m1). apply Hdeg in Hnexp as Hm. destruct (le_dec n MAX). - rewrite <- Hm. reflexivity. - exfalso. lia.
